'''Kunda stones''' had many practical applications in [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] construction, medicine and [[:Category:Communications|communications]]. The use of these stones as a lightsaber [[Focusing lens/Legends|focusing lens]] created a broader beam that allowed the wielder an increase in [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] bolt deflection. Kunda stones also reversed the effects of [[Pacifog]]. They grew and were harvested on the planet [[Kadril]].

